{"tid":726224,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA 12nm/7nm GPU 延遲推出!!預計 7 月份繪圖卡價格再跌 20%","createTime":"2018-07-02T08:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T11:56:29.000Z","uid":70227,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0173cff42f0db5afedd0300754a6694643b13cdb","tid":726224,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:17:53.000Z","msg":"掘礦用繪圖卡由 2017 至 2018 年第一季銷售額的高峰，到 2018 年第二季出現直線下滑，不少消息稱目前全球繪圖卡的庫存還有數百萬，除了讓各大供應商需要降價清空庫存之外，亦讓兩大廠商 AMD 及 NVIDIA 遲遲不推出新一代的繪圖卡。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n根據 DIGITIMES 日前的報導提及，有消息人士指出 7 月份繪圖卡價格預計將平均下降 20% 左右，而採礦 ASIC 訂單急劇放緩也將對台積電 ( TSMC ) 的收入及其 IC 設計產生負面影響。目前，全球繪圖卡市場的庫存數量約為數百萬台，而 NVIDIA 則有大約一百萬台 GPU 等待發佈，相信供應商將推出大幅降價競爭。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nDIGITIMES 亦提到，由於 NVIDIA 繪圖卡的庫存過高，採用台積電 12nm 和 7nm 工藝製造的 NVIDIA 下一代 GPU，預計將推遲至 2018 年第四季度末才推出市場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/16953/掘礦陰霾籠罩NVIDIA_12nm7nm_GPU_延遲推出_預計_7_月份繪圖卡價格再跌_20%25\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F16953%2F%E6%8E%98%E7%A4%A6%E9%99%B0%E9%9C%BE%E7%B1%A0%E7%BD%A9NVIDIA_12nm7nm_GPU_%E5%BB%B6%E9%81%B2%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA_%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88_7_%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BD%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%96%E5%8D%A1%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%86%8D%E8%B7%8C_20%2525&d=jS8%2Bm%2FJlAMZ5KT69m4BQAJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=50378fe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/16953/掘礦陰霾籠罩NVIDIA_12nm7nm_GPU_延遲推出_預計_7_月份繪圖卡價格再跌_20%25</a>"},{"pid":"f9e190e656c9396b52844410ef71007bbfec4b24","tid":726224,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7376fc1cbab3fad956ec9e6fc1ee2158edf57f4b","tid":726224,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:24:47.000Z","msg":"唔出新，即係有新啦，有新就等新...現貨唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4849e8291ad7a7c9b96938d7cf24